as]]\n|-\n! align=\"center\"|[[January 2015 Greek legislative election|January 2015]]\n| 1,718,694\n| 27.9%\n| -1.8\n| {{Composition bar|76|300|hex={{New Democracy (Greece)/meta/color}}}}\n| {{decrease}} 53\n| #2\n| style=\"background:#fcc;\"| Opposition\n| [[Antonis Samaras]]\n|-\n! align=\"center\"|[[September 2015 Greek legislative election|September 2015]]\n| 1,526,205\n| 28.3%\n| +0.4\n| {{Composition bar|75|300|hex={{New Democracy (Greece)/meta/color}}}}\n| {{decrease}} 1\n| #2\n| style=\"background:#fcc;\"| Opposition\n| [[Vangelis Meimarakis]]\n|-\n! align=\"center\"|[[2019 Greek legislative election|2019]]\n| 2,251,411\n| 39.85%\n| +11.55\n| {{Composition bar|158|300|hex={{New Democracy (Greece)/meta/color}}}}\n| {{increase}} 83\n| '''#1'''\n| style=\"background:#cfc;\"| Government\n| [[Kyriakos Mitsotakis]]\n|}\n\n===European Parliament elections ===\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:100%; line-height:16px;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\"|[[European Parliament]]\n|-\n! width=\"60\" | Election\n! width=\"75\" | Votes\n! width=\"45\" | %\n! width=\"45\" | \u00b1[[Percentage point|pp]]\n! width=\"100\" | Seats won\n! width=\"30\" | +/\u2212\n! width=\"30\" | Rank\n! Leader\n|-\n![[1981 European Parliament election in Greece|1981]]\n| 1,779,462\n| 31.3%\n| ''New''\n| {{Composition bar|8|24|hex={{New Democracy (Greece)/meta/color}}}}\n| {{increase}} 8\n| #2\n| [[Georgios Rallis]]\n|-\n![[1984 European Parliament election in Greece|1984]]\n| 2,266,568\n| 38.1%\n| +6.8\n| {{Composition bar|9|24|hex={{New Democracy (Greece)/meta/color}}}}\n| {{increase}} 1\n| #2\n| [[Evangelos Averoff]]\n|-\n![[1989 European Parliament election in Greece|1989]]\n| 2,647,215\n| 40.5%\n| +2.4\n| {{Composition bar|10|24|hex={{New Democracy (Greece)/meta/color}}}}\n| {{increase}} 1\n| #'''1'''\n| [[Constantine Mitsotakis]]\n|-\n![[1994 European Parliament election in Greece|1994]]\n| 2,133,372\n| 32.7%\n| -7.8\n| {{Composition bar|9|25|hex={{New Democracy (Greece)/met